com.swirl

Class SwirlListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.SwirlListener

  • public class SwirlListener
extends java.lang.Object
    SwirlListener is a convenience class created to facilitate intercepting events on the eventBus. Instead of implementing methods annotated with @Subscribe and a single Event object parameter, all of the common events are presented as methods that can be overridden.
